Shoot em Up

The Psychology of Gun Control

Flavio Azevedo

01 August, 2018

1 Gun Control

1.1 Items


  1. Repeal all gun control laws and affirm the right to keep and bear arms
  2. Gun ownership
  3. Gun control laws are not nearly strict enough

All items were asked in 9-point scale raning from 1 (Strongly Disagree) to 9 (Strongly Agree).
